ing was \\\"extremely aggressive\\\", said the IOC.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.999914246326822, \"rank\": 8.521429363414295e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.619020095213542e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ruling\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has now released details about what it described as a \\\"new incident in the Russian disinformation and defamation campaign\\\" against the organisation and Bach, who is a German former Olympic fencer.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.619020095213542e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\", \"score\": 0.9999996780091415, \"rank\": 3.219909022122705e-07, \"text\": \"Russian disinformation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999998828309413, \"rank\": 1.171689660605969e-07, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9585627120481587, \"rank\": 0.04320637681646097, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"new incident\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fake calls purporting to be from the African Union Commission appear to have been made by the very same group that has already attacked a number of global political leaders and other high-ranking personalities in the same way,\\\" said the IOC in a statement.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999962335896715, \"rank\": 3.709912552926592e-06, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.619020095213542e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fake calls\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the very same group\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"global political leaders\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"other high-ranking personalities\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During the calls, a person pretending to be the chair of the African Union Commission wanted to have arguments, in particular from the IOC against the politicisation of sport by the Russian government, in order to prepare a statement against such politicisation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999962335896715, \"rank\": 3.709912552926592e-06, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.619020095213542e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999925723841, \"rank\": 4.398455680013405e-09, \"text\": \"Russian government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Russia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the calls\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"the chair\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"arguments\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"the politicisation\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"fro